        <p>Thank you for joining ThichCungKieng! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Get started by exploring our platform:</p>
        <p>
          <a href='{{url}}' class='button'>Visit ThichCungKieng</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
